data.description: Experience the allure of this exquisite three-bedroom, two-bath home, offering unparalleled views of Pagosa Peak against a backdrop of welcoming aspen trees. This home is situated within walking distance to Born's Lake, close to National Forest trail heads and walking paths for your enjoyment of the outdoors. The home has a double door leading to the fenced back yard for gardening, grilling enjoyment or for your fur babies or your children to play. The owner has put new flooring in the living room which extends down the hallway and into the second bathroom.  A remarkable highlight of this residence is the expansive skylight in the kitchen, bathing the heart of the home in warm, natural light. The open concept living and kitchen area is enhanced by a fresh, white palette, creating an inviting atmosphere. Entertaining is a breeze with both a separate dining area and a central island offering additional seating for large gatherings.  The generously sized master bedroom provides comfort and tranquility.  Stay comfortable year-round with air-conditioning unit and a natural gas furnace, with recently cleaned air ducts ensuring optimal air quality. Not to mention, the convenience of a sprinkler system in both the front and backyard. This residence is a true gem, combining mountain views, outdoor proximity, and interior charm. A two-car garage with a new door provides ample space for your vehicles. Seller is motivated. Come check it out!
